---
description: Defines the preferred order of class members in TypeScript/JavaScript classes
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Class member ordering (top to bottom):
1. Static properties (public, protected, private)
2. Instance properties (public, protected, private)
3. Constructor
4. Static methods (public, protected, private)
5. Instance methods (public, protected, private)

Within each category, order by:
- Public members first
- Protected members second
- Private members last
